          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-X16-1351-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-X16-1351-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-X16-1351-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-X16-1351-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">I</hi>'D have you to know, as sure as you're Dean,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X16-1351-line-2" n="2">On Thursday my cask of Obrien I'll drain:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X16-1351-line-3" n="3">If my wife is not willing, I say she's a quean.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X16-1351-line-4" n="4">And my right to the cellar, I Gad I'll maintain</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X16-1351-line-5" n="5">As bravely as any that fought at Dunblain:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X16-1351-line-6" n="6">Go tell her it over and over again.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X16-1351-line-7" n="7">I hope as I ride to the town, it won't rain;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X16-1351-line-8" n="8">For, should it, I fear it would cool my hot brain,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X16-1351-line-9" n="9">Intirely extinguish my poetic vein;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X16-1351-line-10" n="10">And then I should be as stupid as Kain,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X16-1351-line-11" n="11">Who preach'd on three heads, tho' he mention'd but twain.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X16-1351-line-12" n="12">Now Wardel's in haste, and begins to complain;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X16-1351-line-13" n="13">Your most humble servant, Dear Sir, I remain,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X16-1351-line-14" n="14">
              <space>T. S──────<hi rend="small-caps">N</hi>/hi&gt;.</space>
            </l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X16-1351-line-15" n="15">Get Helsham, Walmsley and Delany,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X16-1351-line-16" n="16">And some Grattans, if there be any <note place="foot">·<hi rend="italics">i.e</hi>. In Dublin, for they were county-clergy, living near the city.</note>,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X16-1351-line-17" n="17">Take care you do not bid too many.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
